USigmund Freud, owazalwa ngoMeyi 6, 1856 eFreiberg (uMbuso Wase-Austria) futhi wafa ngo-September 23, 1939 eLondon, wayengudokotela wezinzwa wase-Austrian, umsunguli we-psychoanalysis.

Udokotela waseViennese, uFreud uhlangana nabantu abambalwa ababalulekile ekuthuthukisweni kwe-psychoanalysis, okuyi-theoretician eyinhloko. Ubungane bakhe noWilhelm Fliess, ukusebenzisana kwakhe noJosef Breuer, ithonya likaJean-Martin Charcot kanye nemibono nge-hypnosis evela eSikoleni seSalpêtrière kuzomholela ekucabangeni kabusha izinqubo zengqondo. Izinto ezimbili ezinkulu azitholile ubulili bezingane kanye nokuquleka. Bamholela ekuthuthukiseni imibono eminingana yeziphathimandla ze-psychic, okokuqala maqondana nomqondo wokuquleka, maqondana namaphupho kanye ne-neurosis, bese uphakamisa indlela yokwelapha, ukwelashwa kwengqondo. Phakathi nohambo lwakhe oluya eMelika ngo-1909, uFreud wabeka izinto eziyisisekelo ze-psychoanalytic ku-Five Lessons on Psychoanalysis3,4. Kungaphakathi kohlaka lokwelapha, kusukela ku-Studies on Hysteria, futhi ikakhulukazi ekuhlaziyeni kwakhe kokuqala "kwecala likaDora", lapho uFreud ethola kancane kancane ukubaluleka kokudluliswa.


UFreud wahlanganisa isizukulwane sama-psychotherapist, isinyathelo ngesinyathelo, sakha i-psychoanalysis, okokuqala e-Austria, Switzerland, Berlin, kwase kuba eParis, eLondon nase-United States. Naphezu kokuhlukana kwangaphakathi nokugxeka, i-psychoanalysis yazisungula njengesiyalo esisha sesayensi yabantu kusukela ngo-1920. Ngo-1938, uFreud, owayesongelwa umbuso wamaNazi, wasuka eVienna waya ekudingisweni eLondon, lapho afa khona ngomdlavuza womhlathi ngo-1939.

Igama elithi “psycho-analysis” livela ngokokuqala ngqá ngo-1896 esihlokweni esabhalwa ngesiFulentshi, esanyatheliswa ngalolu limi ngo-March 30, 1896, kwase kuba ngesiJalimane ngo-May 15, 1896. Kodwa “lezi zihloko ezimbili zathunyelwa ngosuku olufanayo. ” , February 5, 18965. I-Psychoanalysis isekelwe emicabangweni eminingi nemiqondo eyakhiwe noma ethathwe uFreud. "Njengesayensi, i-psychoanalysis ayibonakali ngezinto eziphatha ngayo, kodwa ngendlela esebenza ngayo," ubhala ku-Introduction to Psychoanalysis6,7. Inqubo yokwelapha, kusukela ngo-1898 ngendlela ye-cathartic, no-Josef Breuer, ukuthuthukiswa kwekhambi lokuhlaziya, igalelo eliyinhloko le-psychoanalysis. I-hypothesis yokuqulekile ijulisa i-theorization ye-psyche. Eminye imiqondo izokhula kancane kancane futhi ibe nzima ithiyori ye-psychoanalytic, uFreud ayichaza ngokuthi “isayensi yokuquleka kwengqondo”8, kanye nolwazi lwezinqubo zengqondo nezelapha.


Nakuba eba umuntu ohamba phambili ekhulwini lama-20, uSigmund Freud kwadingeka abhekane nokugxekwa okuningi ngesikhathi sokuphila kwakhe, okufana nokukaKarl Kraus, owenqaba incazelo yobulili yezincwadi zemibhalo, noma eka-Egon Friedell, ofanelekela ukuhlaziywa kwengqondo “kwegama-mbumbulu- Inkolo yamaJuda” kanye “nehlelo”. Ngawo-1990 e-United States, izingxabano emaphephandabeni, ezaziwa ngokuthi i-Freud Wars, zahlasela i-psychoanalysis ngobuntu bukaFreud. Zabuyekezwa e-France eminyakeni eyishumi yokuqala yawo-2000, nge-Black Book of Psychoanalysis kanye nendatshana ka-Michel Onfray, ethi, The Twilight of an Idol. Kodwa ukugxeka okubukhali okubhekiswe kuFreud kanye nethiyori ye-psychoanalytic kuwuhlelo lwe-epistemological: kuhlobene nesayensi ye-psychoanalysis. U-Karl Popper uvame ukucashunwa ngokugxeka kwakhe izitatimende ezingokwengqondo ze-psychoanalysis, azithatha njengesayensi-mbumbulu.

Ngokwenza kanjalo, isiyalo esakhiwe nguFreud, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi sigxekwa noma cha, namuhla sinendawo ebalulekile emasikweni aseNtshonalanga, uma kuphela ukucabangela ukuthandwa kwayo yi-cinema, kuyilapho ezincwadini, ifika "kuyise we-psychoanalysis" avele njengomlingiswa oqanjiwe, njengokuthi Isivakashi sika-Éric-Emmanuel Schmitt.


